Reverse a String :
You are given a string s. You need to reverse the string.
Input:
s = Geeks
Output: skeeG

Approach:
Using two pinter approach, One poinitng to the start of the array and other pointing to the end of the array.
Keep swapping and incrementing both of them till start crosses or becomes equal to end.

Code:
string reverseWord(string str){
  int s=0;
  int len=str.length();
  int e=len-1;
  while(s<=e){
      swap(str[s++],str[e--]);
  }
  return str;
}
